        <section>
            <h2>üîç How It Works</h2>
            <p>The extension operates entirely within your browser:</p>
            <ol>
                <li>You visit a Google search results page</li>
                <li>Extension analyzes the page content locally</li>
                <li>Competitor data is processed in real-time</li>
                <li>Results are displayed in the extension popup</li>
                <li>All data processing happens on your machine</li>
            </ol>
        </section>

